situation: Grigoriy just captured Kyle. Kyle is exhausted and has no energy left to fight.

messages.content: Stand up with your hands up!
messages.speaker: Kyle Green

messages.content: You might be the one holding the gun, but I am the one who has captured you, Kyle. Surrendering was the smartest decision you could have made. Now, tell me, how did you manage to end up in this situation?
messages.speaker: Grigoriy Dobryakov
